post_text: Did you know that studies have proven to show that children can lose up to 50% of what they learned in the previous school year during summer vacation? To assist with the summer slide we are offering parents and K-8 students the opportunity to work with MobyMax. Over the next two weeks, from August 9th through August 23rd, students will be able to login into MobyMax and complete assignments on their current level. Please note that they will use the login for their school during the 19-20 school year. Additionally, their login Username and Password is their Student ID for both entries. To maximize results, we suggest a minimum of 1 hour per day over the next 2 weeks to reduce the summer slide and support building on skills as we prepare to go back to school. For more information visit the district website at www.eht.k12.nj.us. #ehtpride #ehtstrong

post_text:
La devolución de los computadores portátiles Chromebook tendrá lugar el jueves 18 de junio de 10:00 a.m. a 4:00 p.m. y el viernes 19 de junio de 7:00 a.m. a 9:00 a.m.en la escuela Miller. Cuando llegue para devolver el dispositivo, le pedimos que no abandone su vehículo. Un oficial de seguridad lo dirigirá y le pedirá que proporcione el nombre completo y el número de identificación del estudiante.
